casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 20, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

02-103. State ex rel. Martin v. State Med. Bd.

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss and motion to strike motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
